(668, 'Diacerein', 'Osteoarthritis, symptomatic relief from deep achy pain, morning stiffness and muscle spasm.', 'Hypersensitivity. Pregnancy, lactation.', 'Renal impairment.', 'Loose motions, epigastric pain, nausea, vomiting. Discoloration of urine, skin allergy rarely occurs.'),
